---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Ashley Renee Photography" description="Learn more about Ashley Renee, wedding and portrait photographer.">

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[380px] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/couples/DSC01550.jpg"
        alt="About Ashley"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/55 via-black/5 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-14 text-white">
      <p class="font-['Jost'] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-white/70 mb-2">Get to Know Me</p>
      <h1 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond'] text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light">About Ashley</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-[#faf8f5]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/images/couples/DSC08835-3.jpg"
            alt="Ashley Renee"
            class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 border border-[#c4a882] -z-10"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram" class="text-[#7a7470] hover:text-[#c4a882] transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"></circle>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="0.5" fill="currentColor"></circle>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook" class="text-[#7a7470] hover:text-[#c4a882] transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" aria-label="Pinterest" class="text-[#7a7470] hover:text-[#c4a882] transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12c0 4.24 2.65 7.86 6.39 9.29-.09-.78-.17-1.98.03-2.83.19-.77 1.28-5.43 1.28-5.43s-.33-.65-.33-1.62c0-1.52.88-2.65 1.97-2.65.93 0 1.38.7 1.38 1.54 0 .94-.6 2.34-.91 3.64-.26 1.09.54 1.97 1.6 1.97 1.92 0 3.21-2.45 3.21-5.35 0-2.21-1.49-3.76-3.61-3.76-2.46 0-3.9 1.84-3.9 3.75 0 .74.28 1.54.64 1.97.07.08.08.16.06.24l-.24.97c-.04.15-.13.18-.3.11-1.11-.52-1.81-2.14-1.81-3.44 0-2.8 2.03-5.37 5.85-5.37 3.07 0 5.46 2.19 5.46 5.11 0 3.05-1.92 5.5-4.58 5.5-.89 0-1.74-.46-2.03-1.01l-.55 2.07c-.2.77-.74 1.73-1.1 2.32.83.26 1.71.4 2.62.4 5.52 0 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-['Jost'] text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[#c4a882] mb-4">My Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond'] text-4xl font-light text-[#2d2926] mb-6 leading-snug">
          Hi you beautiful souls, I'm Ashley Renee.
        </h2>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-[#c4a882] mb-8"></div>

        <div class="space-y-5 font-['Jost'] text-sm text-[#7a7470] leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm a wife, a mom, a creative, and someone who genuinely enjoys connecting with people. I'm happily married to my best friend, David, and we welcomed our son, Dee, in December 2025. Life these days is a mix of family, creativity, and a little bit of chaos — in the best way.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not behind the camera, I'm usually reading, writing, talking (a lot), or working on some kind of craft. I love creating things with my hands just as much as I love capturing moments. Our home stays full with two dogs, Kao and Kura, and a flock of chickens that keep us stocked with eggs and entertained.
          </p>
          <p>
            I've been a photographer for about 8 years now. I started with landscapes — quiet, still moments — and over time, that grew into capturing weddings and real-life stories. I could give my style a name and dress it up with a bunch of words, but honestly, I'd rather just be me. My photography is an extension of who I am — real, present, and intentional.
          </p>
          <p>
            I love kayaking, home renovations, and anything that lets me build or experience something meaningful. That same mindset carries into my work. I'm here to capture your moments as they are — authentic, personal, and worth remembering.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Fun Facts -->
        <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          {[
            { label: 'Years Experience', value: '8+' },
            { label: 'Weddings Shot', value: '200+' },
            { label: 'Happy Families', value: '500+' },
            { label: 'Cities Traveled', value: '30+' },
          ].map(stat => (
            <div class="text-center p-6 border border-[#e8e4de] bg-white">
              <p class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond'] text-4xl font-light text-[#c4a882] mb-1">{stat.value}</p>
              <p class="font-['Jost'] text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#7a7470]">{stat.label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-[#2d2926] text-white font-['Jost'] text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase px-8 py-3.5 hover:bg-[#c4a882] transition-all duration-300">
            Let's Work Together
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
